  <h2>Architecture</h2> 
  <p>HTML5 forms functionality is deployed as a package within the embedded AEM instance and is exposesd as a REST end point over HTTP/S using RESTful <a href="http://sling.apache.org/" target="_blank">Apache Sling Architecture</a>.</p> 
  <p> </p> 
