  </div> 
  <div>
    HTML5 forms allow developers to create Profile and Profile Renderer to customize the appearance of the forms. For example, HTML forms allow developers to integrate forms in a panel or &amp;lt;div&amp;gt; section of an existing HTML portal. 
  </div> 
